		<button class="collapsible">Expand - Program of Studies</button>
		<div class="content">
			<p>Students develop skills in the proper use of a database management system by developing flat-file databases and demonstrating their use in personal and business applications. <em>Prerequisite: None   </em> </p>
		</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h2><img src="INF2070 Google Classroom 1000-250.png" width="200px"  alt=""/> INF 2070 Database 2 (Access) </h2>
