		<div class="content">
			<p>Students enhance production skills by integrating data from a variety of sources into a finished product.   <em>Prerequisites: INF3060: Word Processing 3, INF2070: Database 2, INF2080: Spreadsheet 2, INF1070: Digital Presentation</em> </p>
		</div>
